al Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-4666-8201-6\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-1-4666-8201-6\">978-1-4666-8201-6</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Gamification%3A+Concepts%2C+Methodologies%2C+Tools%2C+and+Applications%3A+Concepts%2C+Methodologies%2C+Tools%2C+and+Applications&amp;rft.pages=143-&amp;rft.pub=IGI+Global&amp;rft.date=2015-03-31&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-4666-8201-6&amp;rft.au=Management+Association%2C+Information+Resources&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DoWvCCAAAQBAJ%26pg%3DPA143&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARhizomatic+learning\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Major2015-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Major2015_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Claire Howell Major (2 April 2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=_vrVBgAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PA65\"><i>Teaching Online: A Guide to Theory, Research, and Practice</i></a>. JHU Press. pp.&#160;65\u2013. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-4214-1633-5\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-1-4214-1633-5\">978-1-4214-1633-5</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Teaching+Online%3A+A+Guide+to+Theory%2C+Research%2C+and+Practice&amp;rft.pages=65-&amp;rft.pub=JHU+Press&amp;rft.date=2015-04-02&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-4214-1633-5&amp;rft.au=Claire+Howell+Major&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D_vrVBgAAQBAJ%26pg%3DPA65&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARhizomatic+learning\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</spa